  "title": "rangeSlider tooltips overlapping when handles close to each other",
  "body": "The tooltips become unreadable when the upper/lower handles are close to one another.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5360586/52224330-95fd0480-285c-11e9-8d44-7d9cddeaff84.png)\r\n\r\nWould it be possible to provide a single combined tooltip when they would otherwise overlap?\r\nLook at the second example on this page:\r\nhttp://ionden.com/a/plugins/ion.rangeSlider/demo.html\r\n",
